query:
INSERT INTO _files (id, name, path, size, used, created_at, updated_at)
            VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6, $7)
            ON CONFLICT (id) DO UPDATE SET
                name = EXCLUDED.name,
                path = EXCLUDED.path,
                size = EXCLUDED.size,
                used = EXCLUDED.used,
                updated_at = EXCLUDED.updated_at
